So to choose the right form of exercise for you, you need to figure out these 5 factors~

1. GOAL- If your goal is to build strength and muscle, the Gym might be the right choice for you but if you want to focus on overall health & fitness, get slim and release stress & anxiety, Yoga might be the right choice for you

2. INTEREST/PASSION - If you have an interest or passion for any particular exercise form, that will be the right choice for you, Not only it will help you to stay regular at it but you'll also build your skill in your area of interest

3. BUDGET - If you go to Gym, you need to spend heavily on your PT sessions, gym memberships etc. whereas Yoga can be done right at your home with just a yoga mat. 

4. TIME - You need to figure out how much time can you spend every day on your exercise. According to that, you need to choose whether you want to go to the Gym which might be a little away from your home or if you have less time you can choose yoga which you can do right from your home.

5. CONVENIENCE & ACCESSIBILITY - You need to see what is the right exercise for you nearby. You do not want to go very far from your home every day just to exercise

Let me know in the comments what according to you is the best suitable exercise for you👇
